♪ WHAT I'D BE WITHOUT YOU ♪

41:21.000 --> 41:23.500
I TOOK IT BACK.

41:23.542 --> 41:25.166
MY PROPOSAL.

41:25.208 --> 41:27.208
YOU CAN DO THAT?

41:27.250 --> 41:30.041
I DON'T KNOW. (laughs)
BUT I DID.

41:30.083 --> 41:31.291
OH.

41:31.333 --> 41:33.291
I DON'T KNOW.
MAYBE YOU'RE RIGHT.

41:33.333 --> 41:36.917
I HOPE NOT, BUT... I'M GONNA
MAKE IT WORK WITH SAM.

41:36.959 --> 41:38.917
I WILL.

