41:51.000 --> 41:53.417
YEAH.

41:53.458 --> 41:55.750
(laughs) GOD,
WHAT IS WRONG WITH ME, NAI?

41:55.792 --> 41:59.542
(exhales) SO MANY THINGS.
(laughs)

